Package: construe
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to 'Construe'
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
  person("Tomás", "Teijeiro", role = c("aut", "cph")),
  person("Constantino A.", "García", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "constantinoantoniogm@gmail.com")
  )
Description: Interface to 'Construe' <https://github.com/citiususc/construe>, a knowledge-based 
  abductive framework for  electrocardiogram (ECG) signals in terms of the basic waveforms (P, QRS, T)
  to complex rhythm patterns (Atrial fibrillation, Bigeminy, Trigeminy, Ventricular flutter/fibrillation,
  etc.).
Encoding: UTF-8
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/citiususc/construe
BugReports: https://github.com/citiususc/construe/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4)
Imports:
    reticulate (>= 1.2.0.9008), 
    magrittr, 
    dplyr,
    methods,
    R6,
    utils
Suggests: 
    ggplot2,
    testthat, 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Remotes:
    rstudio/reticulate
SystemRequirements: Construe dependencies (https://github.com/citiususc/construe)
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
